{"tid":821541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山竹襲港】表演者尖嘴海傍吹喇叭 八歲細路哥追風：好好玩","createTime":"2018-09-16T03:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T04:05:30.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"75ae99019e0608e3e2879db6231ddbd0981f5b81","tid":821541,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:38:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/818624-香港-【山竹襲港】表演者尖嘴海傍吹喇叭+八歲細路哥追風：好好玩\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F818624-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9%E8%A5%B2%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%91%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94%E8%80%85%E5%B0%96%E5%98%B4%E6%B5%B7%E5%82%8D%E5%90%B9%E5%96%87%E5%8F%AD%2B%E5%85%AB%E6%AD%B2%E7%B4%B0%E8%B7%AF%E5%93%A5%E8%BF%BD%E9%A2%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%BD%E5%A5%BD%E7%8E%A9&d=q8VuwXGZx9zndjUINeKo9%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b95ad47a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F818624-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9%E8%A5%B2%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%91%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94%E8%80%85%E5%B0%96%E5%98%B4%E6%B5%B7%E5%82%8D%E5%90%B9%E5%96%87%E5%8F%AD%2B%E5%85%AB%E6%AD%B2%E7%B4%B0%E8%B7%AF%E5%93%A5%E8%BF%BD%E9%A2%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%BD%E5%A5%BD%E7%8E%A9&h=4c1f62ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/818624-香港-【山竹襲港】表演者尖嘴海傍吹喇叭+八歲細路哥追風：好好玩</a><br />\n<br />\n「山竹」吹襲本港，各區風勢及雨勢增強，天文台呼籲市民盡量留在室內地方。有市民在九號風球情況下，到尖沙嘴天星碼頭附近的海傍吹喇叭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，亦有市民在該處釣魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，姚女士與朋友一早到尖沙咀碼頭釣魚， 稱因打風先有金鼓釣，指平時冇金鼓釣，去街市買要百多元一條，今日更可一次釣兩條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n亦有家長帶小朋友到海傍感受「山竹」威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，今年八歲的廖小朋友指，今次是第二次到海傍感受颱風威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，更明言「好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。"},{"pid":"8b013f5477f74ef8d402c340b1696a185f4888f4","tid":821541,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180916/_2018091610025288548.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180916%2F_2018091610025288548.jpg&h=ee91b994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有表演者於海傍吹喇叭；廖小朋友指，今次是第二次到海傍感受颱風威力。</span></div>"},{"pid":"50369e574c4bdbc5ec8dbb22ff4bfff9cddf5afe","tid":821541,"uid":42625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:41:24.000Z","msg":"達爾文獎候選人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e7da24be72738b818f86fa7639918e4624ffb3","tid":821541,"uid":183486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:41:28.000Z","msg":"吹埋落海仲好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d56647b65d229a59920391663d0381aac1316a","tid":821541,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:41:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180916/_2018091609181351697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180916%2F_2018091609181351697.jpg&h=4b924022&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">表演者天星碼頭吹喇叭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180916/_2018091610025319784.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180916%2F_2018091610025319784.jpg&h=da4eb326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年八歲的廖小朋友指，今次是第二次到海傍感受颱風威力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180916/_2018091609345014441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180916%2F_2018091609345014441.jpg&h=6c2586a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姚小姐在該處釣魚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180916/_2018091609181340805.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180916%2F_2018091609181340805.jpg&h=e1f65218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民風雨下自拍。</span></div>"},{"pid":"a845ee12e9b4a6c7af03949bf9007ea6626d8922","tid":821541,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"735ce2662153e020e6af94b290abe07c28349dab","tid":821541,"uid":59283,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:43:05.000Z","msg":"呢個阿媽真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277c415e578b34e60bdce26e02c47f79c90eafc6","tid":821541,"uid":11097,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:44:08.000Z","msg":"吹撚曬班含家剷落海啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d8698a52b75e86c8ca0557a8ab65852c678616","tid":821541,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:45:15.000Z","msg":"要放上抖音"},{"pid":"b1602da3660c5a2bd6ebf9642640fce0db3e772c","tid":821541,"uid":200474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:46:39.000Z","msg":"到時成個人畀浪扯落海就唔荒唔好玩喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5413e3bc0759ff856336c28afdacd8b9ba00d8c","tid":821541,"uid":42582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:48:22.000Z","msg":"個老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd78c78b51d1caa79fc0d722264ee8